// Ambient declarations for static image imports (*.png, *.svg, *.jpg, ...).
//
// Next.js normally injects these via the git-ignored next-env.d.ts, which is
// only generated by `next dev` / `next build`. CI runs `tsc --noEmit`
// (typecheck) BEFORE the build step, so on a fresh checkout next-env.d.ts does
// not yet exist and the leaflet marker `*.png` imports in
// components/map/MapView.tsx fail with TS2307. Referencing Next's image-types
// here makes those module declarations available during typecheck regardless of
// build ordering. Idempotent with next-env.d.ts (same underlying reference).
/// <reference types="next/image-types/global" />
